{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make people who get paid over \u00a390,000 pay extra 10% tax on second jobs.",
        "additional_details": "I would like Parliament to do this because I feel that it would be a superb way of funding things like to NHS, road maintenance, the military, the care sector, education and investment in community something the current government have been rightly talking about doing.",
        "background": "I would like parliament to introduce a change  in tax law that mandates  individuals who get paid over \u00a390,000 to pay extra income tax on second jobs.  This would bring in a much needed boost to the UK economy.",
